<plot>Kelly, an eight year old girl, believes that she is being stalked by a wolf. It visits her in her dreams and when she is alone. Her mother, Amelia, is struggling to hold her family together. She battles with her rebellious son, Anton, at the expense of looking after Kelly. One night when Anton has left Kelly at home, Amelia, worried and concerned, leaves Kelly to go find him. Kelly alone and confused, begins to realize her wolf may not be a dream after all.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?659679</url></doc>
